A flock of colorful tropical birds perched on interconnected server racks in a lush jungle setting, their feathers gleaming in shades of blue, yellow, and orange, some birds passing small glowing data crystals between them like a network, vines and cables intertwining naturally around the metallic structures, warm golden sunlight filtering through the canopy above, Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures, whimsical and warm atmosphere, detailed foliage with gentle movement suggested in the composition, the birds appearing curious and collaborative as they gather together on their technological perches
